Floor = AFloor or BFloor
Wall = AWall or BWall
Target = ATarget or BTarget
Black = ABlack or BBlack

AObjects = AWall or AFloor or ABlack
BObjects = BWall or BFloor or BBlack

Utility = dock or gutter
Anything = AObjects or BObjects

