======
RULES
======

[ > player | gutter ] -> cancel

( on the first tic, the dock is empty so populate it )
( this rule will only run on the first turn since the dock will never be empty )

[ stationary APlayerOn ] [ dock no AObjects ] -> [ stationary APlayerOn ] [ dock random AObjects ]
[ stationary BPlayerOn ] [ dock no BObjects ] -> [ stationary BPlayerOn ] [ dock random BObjects ]

( when the player presses 'x', switch paradigms )

[ action APlayerOn ] [ ABlack ] -> [ action APlayerOn ] [ BBlack ]
[ action APlayerOn ] [ AWall ] -> [ action APlayerOn ] [ BFloor ]
[ action APlayerOn ] [ AFloor ] -> [ action APlayerOn ] [ BWall ]
[ action APlayerOn ] [ BPlayerOff ] -> [ APlayerOff ] [ BPlayerOn ]
[ action BPlayerOn ] [ BBlack ] -> [ action BPlayerOn ] [ ABlack ]
[ action BPlayerOn ] [ BWall ] -> [ action BPlayerOn ] [ AFloor ]
[ action BPlayerOn ] [ BFloor ] -> [ action BPlayerOn ] [ AWall ]
[ action BPlayerOn ] [ APlayerOff ] -> [ BPlayerOff ] [ APlayerOn ]

( players can push walls, and inactive players within )
rigid [ > Player | Wall ] -> [ > Player | > Wall ]
+ rigid [ > Player | PlayerOff ] -> [ > Player | > PlayerOff ]


( after walls are moved, ensure either a floor or wall is in every cell )
late [ APlayerOn ] [ Floor Wall ] -> [ APlayerOn ] [ Wall ]
late [ APlayerOn ] [ no Floor no Wall no Black no Utility ] -> [ APlayerOn ] [ AFloor ]
late [ BPlayerOn ] [ Floor Wall ] -> [ BPlayerOn ] [ Wall ]
late [ BPlayerOn ] [ no Floor no Wall no Black no Utility ] -> [ BPlayerOn ] [ BFloor ]

( at the end of a tic, move all blocks down, eliminating the bottom row )
( the player needs to remain stationary until the last second, so that all the )
( remaining stationary rules can be run )

( we need to act on the player, so we can't rely on them remaining stationary )
[ update ] [ stationary Player ] -> [ action update ] [ stationary player ]

down [ action update ] [ APlayerOn ] [ no dock AObjects ] -> [ action update ] [ > APlayerOn ] [ no dock > AObjects ]
down [ action update ] [ BPlayerOn ] [ no dock BObjects ] -> [ action update ] [ > BPlayerOn ] [ no dock > BObjects ]

[ action update ] [ anything gutter ] -> [ action update ] [ gutter ]
[ action update ] [ player gutter ] -> [ action update ] [ gutter ]

( repopulate the dock )

( TODO we could reduce the frequency of black tiles )
( by running random again every time a black is chosen, until we run it n times or no black is chosen )

[ action update ] [ APlayerOn ] [ dock no AObjects ] -> [ action update ] [ APlayerOn ] [ dock random AObjects ]
[ action update ] [ BPlayerOn ] [ dock no BObjects ] -> [ action update ] [ BPlayerOn ] [ dock random BObjects ]

[ action update ] -> [ update ]

